@startuml dynamic
title MaiAgent AI Django — 提交訊息 → AI 回覆 → SSE 推播 (補充圖 Dynamic Diagram)

skinparam sequenceMessageAlign center
skinparam maxMessageSize 160
skinparam BoxPadding 10

actor "使用者瀏覽器" as Client
participant "Django API\n(web)" as API
database "PostgreSQL" as DB
queue "Redis\n(broker / channel layer / ticket)" as Redis
participant "Celery Worker" as Worker
participant "Realtime Consumer\n(ASGI)" as SSE
participant "AI Model Provider" as LLM

== 建立 SSE 連線 ==
Client -> API : GET /conversations/{id}/sse-ticket/
API -> Redis : issue_ticket(conversation_id)
Redis --> API : ticket
API --> Client : { ticket }

Client -> SSE : GET /sse/conversations/{id}/?ticket=...
SSE -> Redis : consume_ticket(ticket)
SSE -> DB : 查詢初始訊息快照
SSE --> Client : text/event-stream(初始快照)

== 提交訊息 ==
Client -> API : POST /conversations/{id}/messages/\n{ content }
API -> DB : select_for_update 檢查狀態機\n(closed / pending_human / reply_in_progress)
API -> DB : 建立 user message(completed)\n+ ai message(pending)
API -> Worker : generate_ai_reply.delay(ai_message_id)
API --> Client : 202 Accepted\n{ user_message_id, ai_message_id }

== 非同步產生 AI 回覆 ==
Worker -> DB : 讀取 Scene / ModelRoute 設定
Worker -> LLM : 透過 litellm.Router 請求回覆\n(依 order/weight 選模，可容錯重試)

alt 成功
    LLM --> Worker : 回覆內容
    Worker -> DB : 更新 ai message = completed\n(content, model_used)
else 失敗且重試耗盡
    LLM --> Worker : 失敗
    Worker -> DB : 更新 ai message = failed(error_message)
    Worker -> DB : Conversation.status = pending_human
end

Worker -> Redis : channel_layer.group_send\n(conv_{id}, 狀態變化事件)
Redis -> SSE : group_send 轉發
SSE --> Client : text/event-stream(狀態變化事件)

@enduml
